annotation.text:
There were many different line-ups of the Charlie Parker Quintet

The 1947-1948 lineup ([artist:c7356af9-9ea6-4a78-a55b-c73775716312|Charlie Parker] Alto Saxophone, [artist:561d854a-6a28-4aa7-8c99-323e6ce46c2a|Miles Davis] Trumpet, [artist:18288a13-0259-4a44-a9dc-558229fbfdd2|Duke Jordan] Piano, [artist:0b6aea55-d855-4a33-ae08-b0280dd28684|Max Roach] Drums, [artist:7d606f44-a90c-4c1e-909d-37e57681a3cf|Tommy Potter] Double Bass) is sometimes referred to as the "Original Charlie Parker Quintet".
